sequenceDiagram
participant Developer
participant CICD as CI/CD Pipeline Subsystem
participant Orchestrator as Deployment Orchestrator Subsystem
participant PMS as Production Management System
participant MMS as Monitoring & Maintenance System
participant Cloud

Developer->>Developer: Implement new feature in PMS/MMS
Developer->>CICD: Commit and push code
CICD->>CICD: Run automated tests
CICD->>CICD: Build Docker image
CICD->>CICD: Verify software compatibility
CICD-->>Orchestrator: Build successful, ready for deployment
Orchestrator->>Orchestrator: Plan incremental rollout
Orchestrator->>PMS: Deploy updated PMS services (phase 1)
PMS-->>Orchestrator: Deployment successful
Orchestrator->>Orchestrator: Validate PMS deployment health
Orchestrator->>MMS: Deploy updated MMS services (phase 2)
MMS-->>Orchestrator: Deployment successful
Orchestrator->>Orchestrator: Validate MMS deployment health
Orchestrator->>Cloud: Update cloud deployment
Cloud-->>Orchestrator: Confirm updates
Orchestrator-->>Developer: Deployment complete (99.99% uptime maintained)
